ared to have the morning off<br />\n2) Have a solid, reliable internet connection NO PHONES<br />\n3) Join our Google Hangout around 10:30AM, Its the same hangout we always use, but I will post the link.<br />\n4) Open your Ticket Invitation link around 11:00AM<br />\n5) Wait patiently<br />\n6) Let everyone know your ticket status as soon as possible<br />\n7) Always buy two tickets<br />\n8) Don\'t buy any more carpasses, we have a ton<br />\n9) Good Luck, and may the force be with you!<br />\n<br />\nIf you have ANY questions please a text at (415) 818-0287 or email me directly at trailblazer@mycodelicforest.org. (That phone number is for texting only, and is specific for our camp)<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- Trailblazer<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Trevor Bice</p>',1,0,0,1,NULL,NULL,1,2,'2018-03-27 06:18:38','2018-03-27 06:20:29',2,'2018-03-27 06:22:00',2,'2018-03-27 06:20:29',1,NULL,0,'Public Pages',NULL,1,NULL,'13dd56c027d5ade7',NULL,'automatic',NULL);
